        <abstract> 
<p>Sends an article ["Des lumières que la géologie peut jeter sur … l’histoire ancienne des Athéniens"] extracted from his work [<hi rend="italic">Animaux fossiles et géologie de l’Attique</hi> (1862–7)]. CD’s letters have been an encouragement.</p> 
            <p>Hopes the belief in transformation will gradually be accepted. For himself the idea in no way undermines his idea of spirituality and his respect for human dignity.</p> 
<p>Hopes to continue his work on the genealogical relationship (<hi rend="italic">enchaînement</hi>) of fossils.</p> 
        </abstract>
